长租公寓“威胁”填表遭质疑 部分长租公寓停止冻结门锁政策。
Long-rented apartments "threatened" to fill out the form have been challenged by some long-rented apartments to stop freezing the lock policy.
饶贤君2020-02-02 16:04。
Rap Yin-jun 2020-02-02 16: 04
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 饶贤君尽管北京市人民政府副秘书长陈蓓在2月1日表态，所有返京人员在接受了相应的医学观察和体温检测后，社区、村、物业部门，无权自行阻止返京人员进入小区，但返京租户的回家路依然面临阻碍。
Although Deputy Secretary-General Chen Bei of the Beijing Municipal People's Government said on Feb. 1 that all returning residents have the right to prevent their return to Beijing by themselves after receiving medical observation and body temperature tests.
。
.
自如、相寓等长租公寓企业最近几日相继要求，租客必须在指定日期前完成返程核心信息填写，否则将冻结智能密码锁。
In recent days, the tenants must complete the core information of the return trip before the appointed date. Otherwise, the smart password lock will be frozen.
。
.
智能密码锁，这一长租公寓的服务内容，可能变成租户回家的门槛。
Intelligent password locks, the service content of this long-rented apartment, could become a threshold for tenants to return home.
。
.
自如在《致全国自如客和业主》的通知中称，全面开启自如APP、小程序、公众号等渠道，请每一位自如客于2月1日前将最近居留地、个人健康、返程日期等核心信息进行提报，自如将与政府相关部门一起进行分类分级管理，逾期提交将被暂时收回居住房屋的智能门锁权限。
In a notice to ease visitors and homeowners across the country, all-purpose APPs, apps, public numbers and the like are invited to report core information such as last place of residence, personal health, date of return, etc. By February 1, they will be able to categorize and rank with the relevant government departments and submit the smart locks for temporary repossession of their homes.
。
.
除自如外，相寓、蛋壳也曾发布过类似措施。
In addition to the ease, Xiangxiang, eggshell has issued similar measures.
。
.
据悉，长租公寓此举是为了响应北京市《关于加强本市租赁中介行业疫情防控工作的通知》，该通知要求，各房地产经纪机构、住房租赁企业要配合社区摸排往来人员情况，向社区提供出租房屋和承租人动态信息。
It is reported that the long-rent apartment is in response to Beijing's "Notice on Strengthening the Prevention and Control of the Municipal Leasing Intermediary Industry," which requires real estate agencies and housing rental enterprises to cooperate with the community in mapping the flow of people, to provide the community with rental housing and tenant dynamics information.
。
.
最近一周，已有多位返京租户被拦在小区门外，北京市人民政府副秘书长陈蓓在2月1日明确，所有返京的人员在接受了相应的医学观察和体温检测后，社区、村、物业部门，无权自行阻止返京人员进入小区。
Chen Bei, deputy secretary-general of the Beijing Municipal People's Government, made it clear on February 1 that after receiving medical observation and body temperature tests, the community, village and property authorities had no right to prevent the returning residents from entering the district.
。
.
配合疫情防控是社会共识，但长租公寓的具体举措却引发了热议。
Coordination with the epidemic prevention and control is a social consensus, but the concrete measures of long-term rental apartments have triggered heated debate.
。
.
很多租客认为，登记信息确实应当配合，但强制收回智能门锁权限、冻结密码锁的行为不合理，是一种“威胁手段”。
Many tenants believe that the registration information should indeed cooperate, but the compulsory withdrawal of smart lock privileges, the behavior of freezing password locks is unreasonable, is a "threat means."
。
.
北京春林律师事务所主任、合伙人庞九林认为，长租公寓冻结租客门锁，具体属于合同问题还是侵权问题，无法确定，但从法律上来讲，长租公寓没有权利执行这一操作，“如果住户在里边不能出来，侵犯了人身自由权，如果住户不能进去，我觉得侵犯了财产权利”。
Pang Jiulin, director and partner of the Beijing Chunlin Law Firm, said that it was not possible to determine whether the long-rent apartment was a contractual or tort issue, but legally, the long-rented apartment was not entitled to perform the operation.
。
.
相寓方面回应，为了保障租客权益，已经对冻结门锁的措施进行整改，并延长了租客提报问卷信息的时间，以提醒、强化、鼓励的方式让租客主动填写问卷。
In response, to protect tenants' rights and interests, measures to freeze door locks have been revamped and tenants have been given more time to submit questionnaires to remind, strengthen and encourage tenants to take the initiative in filling out the questionnaires.
。
.
蛋壳方面表示，此前为了鼓励租客录入信息，曾经误发过类似的信息，但蛋壳很快就予以撤销，改为以鼓励、沟通的方式获取租户的配合，“租客的配合度还是很高的”。
In order to encourage tenants to enter information, the eggshell has been sent similar messages, but the shell was quickly withdrawn and replaced with encouragement and communication to obtain tenants' cooperation, "the tenant's cooperation is still high."
。
.
自如方面表示，自如是为了配合卫健、街道、社区及其他相关部门收集信息，做好疫情配合工作，收集疫情直接关联信息是为了保障客户和其他公民的健康，不为他用，核心是大家的安全，冻结门锁只是督促手段，如果租客未填写，会有多次人工确认相关行程调查，也会根据客户实际情况去沟通。
In order to protect the health of customers and other citizens and not for other purposes, the core is the safety of all. The freezing of door locks is only a means of urging people to confirm the relevant itinerary investigation many times if the tenant fails to fill in the form and communicate according to the actual situation of the customer.
。
.
对于是否涉及侵权，自如方面未正面回应，而是强调，在疫情的特殊情况下，安全引导更为重要。
There was no positive response as to whether violations were involved. Instead, it was emphasized that security guidance was more important in the particular context of the epidemic.
。
.
